\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What has the Ministry of Sports or the Athletics Federation of Nigeria done for the athletes to make sure that they are in the best shape for the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Ministry\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1966}, {\"ngram\": \"the Athletics Federation\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigeria\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"the best shape\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So if you look into all these things, then we would now understand that the Nigerian athletes gave their best; unfortunately they did not have the best of preparation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all these things\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"the Nigerian athletes\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the way forward to ensure that Team Nigeria does better in subsequent competitions, Afolabi added: \\\"Nigeria's Sports Federation needs to stop having this lackadaisical attitude towards the welfare and competitiveness of the athletes.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9975095482194459, \"rank\": 0.00249666961591897, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2350, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ola_Afolabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Afolabi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ola_Afolabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ola_Afolabi\"}, {\"begin\": 2366, \"end\": 2373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9975095482194459, \"rank\": 0.00249666961591897, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"subsequent competitions\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"this lackadaisical attitude\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"the welfare\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"competitiveness\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nigerian athletes need to be given the best of preparation and make sure that they are in the best shape for the Olympics because it is a major tournament.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nigerian athletes\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"the best shape\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"a major tournament\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A major tournament like the Olympics should not be thrown under the carpet.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A major tournament\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"the carpet\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics need the best preparation, unfortunately Team Nigeria have not had the best preparation and it is very sad.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2797, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9975095482